Microscope is black black and silver metal with "U-shaped" base, two eyepieces, adjustable frame with focusing knobs, four lenses of increasing strength mounted on a circular wheel., and a mirror under viewing plate to use as a light source.  Maker's mark, "AO[inside shield shape] on body of microscope in two places, under eye pieces and under viewing plate.  Eyepiece mark has "SPENCER" under the maker's mark and the mark under the viewing plate has "SPENCER/ MADE IN U.S.A./ 748".  Also marked with serial number on curved part of "U-shaped" base, "325887".
